<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It has no connection to the advancement of the plot. I feel it was more a fancy of Sidney Sheldon; to play about with the two girls.<br/><a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It has no connection to the advancement of the plot. I feel it was more a fancy of Sidney Sheldon; to play about with the two girls.<br /><a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
