<span id="freeTextContainer10507105755529631842">Four deaths in last 24 hours. All looked like suicide. But were they?? <br/>The protagonists are two ladies trying to find out the reason of death of their husbands, also trying to save their own lives as well. <br/>This book is a page turner. The cat and mouse chase will keep you on the hook till the last chapters. <br/><br/>Didn&apos;t give 5 stars, because I felt few things were exaggerated.<br/><br/>Nevertheless, this book is worth the read. !!</span>
  <span id="freeText10507105755529631842" style="display:none">Four deaths in last 24 hours. All looked like suicide. But were they?? <br />The protagonists are two ladies trying to find out the reason of death of their husbands, also trying to save their own lives as well. <br />This book is a page turner. The cat and mouse chase will keep you on the hook till the last chapters. <br /><br />Didn't give 5 stars, because I felt few things were exaggerated.<br /><br />Nevertheless, this book is worth the read. !!</span>
